<!DOCTYPE html>
  <head>
    <title>OrigamiMobile</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all'%>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application'%>
  </head>

  <body>
  
  <div data-role="page" data-theme="b">

        <div data-role="header">
            <h1><%= yield :titulo %></h1>
            <%= yield :botones %>
        </div>

        <div class="ui-content" role="main">
                <%= yield %>
        </div>

        <div data-role="footer" data-position="fixed">
            <div data-role="navbar">

    <ul >

          <li> <%= link_to 'Nosotros', root_path,class: "ui-btn ui-btn-icon-top ui-icon-info #{ @origamis.present? ? '' : 'ui-btn-active'} ", data: {ajax: "false"} %></li>

          <li><%= link_to 'Origamis', origamis_path,  class: "ui-btn ui-btn-icon-top ui-icon-bars  #{ @origamis.present? && params[:favoritos].nil? ? 'ui-btn-active' : ''} " , data: {ajax: "false"} %></li>
          
          <li><%= link_to 'Origamis', origamis_path(favoritos: true),  class: "ui-btn ui-btn-icon-top ui-icon-star  #{ params[:favoritos].present? ? 'ui-btn-active' : ''} " , data: {ajax: "false"} %></li>></li>

    </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    <div data-role="page" data-theme="b" id="about">

        <div data-role="header" data-add-back-btn="true">
            <h1>Chips & Ketchup</h1>
        </div>

        <div>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. A aliquid amet at blanditiis consequatur
            cupiditate deserunt dicta ea enim error et explicabo fuga hic illum impedit, iste itaque iure neque odio
            optio, perspiciatis quam quasi qui ratione similique tempore veritatis?
        </div>

        <div data-role="footer" data-position="fixed">
            <div data-role="navbar">
                <ul >
                    <li><a href="#about" data-transition="slide" class="ui-btn ui-btn-icon-top ui-icon-info">About us!</a></li>
                    <li><a href="chips.html" class="ui-btn ui-btn-icon-top ui-icon-bars"
                     data-ajax="false">Chips!</a></li>
                    <li><a href="chips.html?favs=true" class="ui-btn ui-btn-icon-top ui-icon-star"
                    data-ajax="false">Favourite chips!</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
  </body>
</html>
